ng-class-odd :

used to add the css class to the odd rows of table.

ng-class-even:

used to add the css class to the even rows of table.

Syntax:

ng-class-odd / ng-class-even = "css class"

ng-if:

Used to write the if conditions in Angular JS

Syntx:

ng-if="true"/"false"


ng-show/ng-hide:

-used to show / hide the elements based on the conditions


syntax:

ng-show/ng-hide = "true"/"false"




